nodes.text: Kucedre's fate is unclear, as it is possible for the vessel to escape or be destroyed, depending on a number of situations made possible by random AI events in Star Wars: X-Wing Alliance, as well as the actions of the player. Adding further ambiguity to the situation is the fact that not only does Kucedre only appear in X-Wing Alliance, it does not reappear at any point during the rest of the campaign.
